  "title": "Hotel Housekeeping Attendant",
  "description": "<p>RESPONSIBILITIES:</p><p>• Cleans guestrooms and replenishes room amenities according to the operational standards.</p><p>• Anticipate guests’ needs, respond promptly and acknowledge all guests, however busy and whatever time of day.</p><p>• Maintain positive guest relations at all times.</p><p>• Perform thorough cleaning duties and responsible for the cleanliness and maintenance of his work are</p><p>• Report about any defect in room, any damage and any lost & found item left in checked out rooms.<br /></p><p>Salary: $2500 - $3500<br />12 hours work, 1 off day<br /><br />No experience is required as training will be provided.</p><p>Interested please send CV to vel@jalley.com.sg<br /></p><p>Vel Heng Jee Ting (R1108267)<br />Jobs Alley Pte Ltd (21C0599)</p>",
